The next phase (Phase 1 of the **Implementation Guide**) involves building the first functional components:

1. **`core/state.py`** вЂ” `PipelineState` TypedDict (shared state schema)
2. **`core/llm.py`** вЂ” LLM client factory (OpenAI / Gemini / Ollama)
3. **`agents/base_agent.py`** вЂ” Abstract base class with self-healing code execution
4. **`tools/code_executor.py`** вЂ” Sandboxed Python code execution
5. **`tools/file_manager.py`** вЂ” Dataset and artifact file management
6. **`agents/data_profiler.py`** вЂ” First agent: Data Profiler
7. **`core/orchestrator.py`** вЂ” Minimal LangGraph pipeline (Profiler only)
8. **`api/main.py`** вЂ” FastAPI with `POST /upload` endpoint
9. **`ui/app.py`** вЂ” Streamlit upload page + profile viewer
